          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Local Taxpayer Protection Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill requires certain hydropower facility licensees to make an annual payment of $1.8 million to the county in which the licensed hydropower facility is located. Subsequent payments must increase by 2% of the preceding annual payment.</p> <p>The fee applies to a state, or a subdivision of the state, that (1) received a license for a pumped-storage facility, and (2) filed for the license in April 2017. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-03-06T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
